.TH "SYMBOL.ASYNCDISPOSE" "3JS" "August 2, 2025" "JavaScript" "JavaScript Reference Manual"
.SH NAME
Symbol.asyncDispose \- Symbol.asyncDispose
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]Symbol.asyncDispose\f[B]\f[R] static data property
represents the well\-known symbol \f[CR]Symbol.asyncDispose\f[R].
The \f[CR]await using\f[R] declaration looks up this symbol on the
variable initializer for the method to call when the variable goes out
of scope.
.SH VALUE
The well\-known symbol \f[CR]Symbol.asyncDispose\f[R].
.PP
.TS
tab(@);
l l.
T{
